data.description: Welcome home! This 3 bed 2.5 bath traditional home lives large, with space for whatever your needs.  The main level features hardwoods and multiple living spaces along with newly replaced decks on the front and rear. Upstairs you'll find a large primary suite with walk in closet and ensuite bath.  Two secondary bedrooms and a full bath finish out the space.  With a full basement, this home has space for even more activities, such as a workshop, game room, bedroom, or whatever you need. The setting couldn't be more idyllic, situated in a quiet cul-de-sac on a wide and level lot with wooded privacy in the back.  Located close to shopping, library, and parks.
